data.description: Spacious 5 bedrooms/3 bathrooms home with a flex room. Eat-in kitchen features 42' white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and large island. Kitchen and dining room area open to a spacious family room. The home is located in a well-established community in  Villa Rica, GA, that boasts amenities galore, including a 13-acre Amenity Park, paved walking and biking trails, a garden area, an amphitheater for movie nights, and proximity to a golf course, shopping and restaurant.
